  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the potential therapeutic benefit of catheter-based renal
      sympathetic denervation using therapeutic unfocussed ultrasound in a single-arm feasibility
      trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
